data.description: Come see this well-maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with a split floor plan. It is beautifully landscaped with excellent curb appeal. This home has a large living area with vaulted ceilings and a gas-log fireplace. Enjoy cooking in the large kitchen with lots of cabinet and counter space. The enclosed back patio provides over 170 sq ft of extra living space that could be a second living area, office, or kid's playroom. The large backyard has a gazebo to enjoy.
